Functions   02-02-2021
•	It is a reusable code
•	It is a group of statements
Naming conventions
1. name should start with alphabet(Lowercase)
2. camel case rule(getMyHome)
3. No spaces in between(use _ underscore)
Steps
1. definition(process)
2. calling(execution)
